        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "In Him no south or north;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "But one great fellowship of love"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Throughout the whole wide earth."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "In Him shall true heart everywhere"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Their high communion find;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "His service is the golden cord"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Close binding all mankind."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Join hands, then, brothers of the faith,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Whateâ€™er your race may be."
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Who serves my Father as a son"
        },
        {
